üåç Platforms to Apply

1. LinkedIn Jobs

Filter by: Visa Sponsorship / Relocation Assistance.

Many companies in Europe, Canada, and Australia mention relocation packages directly in job posts.



2. Glassdoor & Indeed (Global)

Use location filters (Canada, Germany, Netherlands, UK, Australia, Singapore, etc.).

Search with terms like "visa sponsorship", "relocation package".



3. Wellfound (formerly AngelList Talent)

Focused on startups worldwide.

Many startups in Germany, Netherlands, and Canada hire from India and sponsor visas.



4. Relocate.me

Specializes in jobs that include relocation assistance and visa sponsorship.

Popular for Europe (Germany, Netherlands, Sweden).



5. Stack Overflow Jobs (check availability for your region)

Tech-specific jobs, often with sponsorship options.



6. Global Tech Companies Career Pages

Companies like Amazon, Microsoft, Google, Meta, Booking.com, Zalando, SAP, Atlassian openly sponsor relocation and visas.

Apply directly on their official career sites.



7. Job Boards for Specific Countries

Canada: Job Bank Canada, VanHack (focuses on connecting developers with Canadian jobs + relocation).

Germany & EU: EU Blue Card job boards, Honeypot.io (tech-focused).

Australia: Seek.com.au (filter for visa sponsorship).

UK: UK Government Skilled Worker visa job listings.





